question - https://www.codewars.com/kata/5a53a17bfd56cb9c14000003/train/python

solution 

def disarium_number(number):
    total = 0
    
    for i, num in enumerate(str(number)):
        total += int(num)**(i + 1)
        
    if total == number:
        return 'Disarium !!'
    
    return 'Not !!'
